WEBVTT

00:11:55.553 --> 00:12:00.164
And it is not enough to say
that you will do better in the future.

00:12:00.973 --> 00:12:05.283
Because to have any hope
of stopping this from happening again,

00:12:05.307 --> 00:12:07.679
we have to know the truth.

00:12:09.362 --> 00:12:12.091
And maybe you think,
"Well, it was just a few ads.

00:12:12.489 --> 00:12:14.869
And people are smarter than that, right?"

00:12:16.330 --> 00:12:18.576
To which I would say,
"Good luck with that."

00:12:20.314 --> 00:12:23.617
Because what the Brexit vote demonstrates

00:12:23.641 --> 00:12:26.323
is that liberal democracy is broken.

00:12:27.450 --> 00:12:28.600
And you broke it.